    "Despite their promise, the path to integrating these technologies into clinical practice and drug discovery is laden with hurdles:",
    "• Data Quality, Collection, and Management: As we mentioned before, the strength of DTs is based on their structured data entry and their underlying algorithm.",
    "Therefore, gathered data should be standardized and reported digitally to facilitate comparability.",
